              <div className="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                <p className="font-bold text-slate-300 mb-1">Provisioning Scope</p>
                This account will be registered on the <span className="text-indigo-400 font-mono">agiliumtrade.agiliumtrade.ai</span> cluster. 
